  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan and add chopped onion. Sauté for about 2 minutes until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic to the pan, cook for another minute, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in tamarind paste, tomato puree, and water. Cook for 5 minutes, allowing flavors to meld.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix coriander seeds with cayenne pepper powder and chilli flakes. Sprinkle this mixture over the sauce.",
    "Bring the sauce to a simmer and add tamarind balls. Simmer for an additional 10 minutes until thickened.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or over steamed vegetables."
